"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"*This article explains how you can create a MetaMask wallet that can store cryptocurrency and NFTs.*\\n\\nFollow these instructions to set up your MetaMask wallet:\\n\\n1. **[Click here to download MetaMask](https://metamask.io/download/)** using mobile application or desktop browser extension\\n2. Open the application and get started to **create a new wallet**\\n3. **Set your password** for your new wallet\\n4. **Write down your seed phrase**. It is best to store this written on a safe piece of paper or device that is not connected to the internet. If you forget your password, you can reset it by importing your wallet using your seed phrase. If you loose your seed phrase, it can never be recovered.\\n5. **Complete the seed phrase verification** and account setup steps and voila, you now have a cryptocurrency wallet that supports storing NFTs!\\n\\n**Your public wallet address** is the unique identifier for your wallet. You can easily copy it from below you account name or from the MetaMask menu options.\\n\\n![Where yo view your public wallet address](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/xC9Etz4G5PF4-RgvOHZK7.jpg?height=904&width=1598)\\n\\n**Hint 1 -** **We recommended also setting up the MetaMask browser extension** for an easier experience interacting with websites.\\n\\n**Hint 2 - Pin the MetaMask browser extension to your chrome taskbar.** You can open the the wallet from your browserâ€™s extension menu and pin it to your taskbar for easy access.\\n\\n![Screenshot of how to open MetaMask using the Google Chrome extension](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4BMSVyhTXzXw9swFJU13s.png?height=413&width=764)\\n\\n![MetaMask is now pinned to your taskbar](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/LjjyTxNLlzG5SO_a7srPT.png?height=145&width=435)\\n\\n### View step by step screenshots below\\n\\n*Updated January 20th, 2022*\",\"timestamp\":1642670868,\"title\":\"How to create a MetaMask wallet\"},\"digest\":\"tkwqmjVHggacIxNTqiDsln_pyAFwTHBjMolco0A3tG4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x5056596726deAcAA6a78Ad4f1bB826d008689606\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"sOuV983r5KC3mMgUt6lwHxpSh98Irc9LRL5kAA5yPQY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Tc8itbnJuOsmIdiGa6lDYe6rVVweQ_uTEODW_0HQJt4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"BRClVMKhl15jIeUedzUdsR6494L8vqdPbXzyAo-AoRoBx0y_LMT1bjG60gnoQXLovuFnZlXAy3hc1aq906Kwhg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x437e72951c439881e4f77d6ad8e87a126213d0dd8ba8d2bd5b8ea1c5928e9ac452a548eb879a86f76c01e1fafb59e0de222116e229ccb65dbeb012accac40f681b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"sOuV983r5KC3mMgUt6lwHxpSh98Irc9LRL5kAA5yPQY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Tc8itbnJuOsmIdiGa6lDYe6rVVweQ_uTEODW_0HQJt4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"bUs061SePuOcvbIwSqeNtUgTfGbrsKzYEFZokfv6Tho\"}"